								"type": "text",
								"text": "La Trobada is a homage to Mediterranean culture, flavor, and warmth. This small neighborhood restaurant operated by Inma and Jonathan functions as a gathering space for locals and friends. The name 'La Trobada' (Catalan for 'meeting point') reflects the Mediterranean lifestyle characterized by warmth and shared moments."
